sequenceDiagram
    participant Admin as Administrateur
    participant Browser as Navigateur
    participant Gateway as API Gateway
    participant OrderSvc as Order Service
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    Admin->>Browser: Sélectionne période (7j / 30j / 12m)
    Browser->>Gateway: GET /api/orders/admin/stats?period=7d
    Gateway->>OrderSvc: Forward request + JWT

    OrderSvc->>DB: SELECT date, COUNT, SUM<br/>WHERE created_at >= now() - 7d<br/>GROUP BY date
    DB-->>OrderSvc: Données par jour

    OrderSvc->>DB: SELECT plat_name, COUNT, SUM<br/>GROUP BY plat_name<br/>ORDER BY count DESC
    DB-->>OrderSvc: Top plats vendus

    OrderSvc->>DB: SELECT status, COUNT<br/>GROUP BY status
    DB-->>OrderSvc: Répartition par statut

    OrderSvc->>DB: SELECT EXTRACT(HOUR), COUNT<br/>GROUP BY hour
    DB-->>OrderSvc: Distribution horaire

    OrderSvc-->>Gateway: { daily, topPlats, byStatus, byHour }
    Gateway-->>Browser: 200 OK

    Browser->>Admin: Mise à jour Recharts graphiques
